trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of instances of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 代表執行個體的集合<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別無法被繼承。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> to the end of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 將指定<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref>結尾<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"> </xref>来加入至集合。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index where the mimePart parameter has been added.
trans-unit.target: 以零為起始的索引位置 mimePart 已新增參數。

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether the specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> is a member of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 傳回值，指出是否指定<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref>隸屬<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> to check for collection membership.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"> </xref>來檢查集合成員資格。

trans-unit.source: if the mimePart parameter is a member of the ; otherwise, .
trans-unit.target: 如果 mimePart 參數所屬的 ，否則 。

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection"></xref> to a compatible one-dimensional array of type <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref>, starting at the specified zero-based index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: 複製整個<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection"></xref>到相容的一維陣列的型別<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"> </xref>，從目標陣列的指定以零為起始的索引處開始。

trans-unit.source: An array of type <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> serving as the destination for the copy action.
trans-unit.target: 類型的陣列<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref>做為複製動作的目的端。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which to start placing the copied collection.
trans-unit.target: 以零為起始的索引處開始放置複製的集合。

trans-unit.source: Searches for the specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> and returns the zero-based index of the first occurrence within the collection.
trans-unit.target: 搜尋指定<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref>和傳回集合內第一個出現項目以零為起始的索引。

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> for which to search the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"> </xref>要搜尋<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: A 32-bit signed integer.
trans-unit.target: 32 位元帶正負號的整數。

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> to the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection"></xref> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 將指定<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref>至<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection"></xref>指定索引處。

trans-unit.source: If the number of items in the collection already equals the collection's capacity, the capacity is doubled by automatically reallocating the internal array before the new element is inserted.
trans-unit.target: 如果已經在集合中的項目數等於集合的容量，容量加倍插入新項目之前，會自動重新配置內部的陣列。

trans-unit.source: If the `index` parameter is equal to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>, the `mimePart` parameter is added to the end of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection>.
trans-unit.target: 如果`index`參數等於<xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>、`mimePart`參數加入至<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection>結尾</xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: The elements after the insertion point move down to accommodate the new element.
trans-unit.target: 向下移動以容納新項目插入點後的項目。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which to insert the `mimePart` parameter.
trans-unit.target: 要插入的以零為起始的索引`mimePart`參數。

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"> </xref>来加入至集合。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the value of a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> at the specified zero-based index.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定值<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref>指定以零為起始的索引處。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> whose value is modified or returned.
trans-unit.target: 以零為起始的索引<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref>修改或傳回其值。

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_MimePart" name="MimePart" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_MimePart" name="MimePart" href=""></xref>.

trans-unit.source: Removes the first occurrence of the specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> from the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 移除指定的第一個出現<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref>從<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: This method performs a linear search; therefore, the average execution time is proportional to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會執行線性搜尋;因此，平均執行時間是成比例<xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>.</xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: The elements that follow the removed `MimePart` move up to occupy the vacated spot.
trans-unit.target: 請依照下列所移除的項目`MimePart`向上移動以佔用空出的位置。

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> to remove from the collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"> </xref>若要從集合中移除。
